column5: head to lac seul in 21 days and the wait is killing me how do I make the next 3 weeks fly by so I can fish one of the best walleye lakes in canada
I know how you feel. We will be on Lac Seul four weeks from today. Can't wait to get to Onaway Lodge.
Can't wait. Leaving this Friday for Fisherman's Cove on the great Lac Seul!
26 days to Silver Water Wheel on Lac Seul -- already having trouble sleeping...

Hmmm....how to pass the time. Pack, repack and pack again every 3rd day. Review your packing list, then recheck again. Spool new line, then change your mind and go with braid, then change it back. Tie up some in line spinner rigs, all of your own making, color and style, don't worry you probably will either not use them or lose them with in the first day or 2 anyway. These answers to your dilemma come from years of going thru the same thing. have fun and be safe.
Still have 59 days to go till my moose/fishing trip to Canada. I think I have everything gathered and packed!
15 days for me. Lost Island Lodge. First Canada trip, pumped!
I'm in the waiting phase as well but its for next years trip as this ones all ready out of the way.
The wait is over. Lac Seul here we come!!!
